						"description": "## Create Customer\n\nCreates a new customer in the system.\n\n### Authentication\nMust come through the API Gateway (headers `X-User-Id`, `X-Internal`).\n\n### Request Body\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `cedula` | string | Yes | National ID. Must be unique. Max 20 chars. |\n| `full_name` | string | Yes | Customer's full name. Max 100 chars. |\n| `address` | string | Yes | Customer's address. Max 200 chars. |\n| `phone` | string | Yes | Phone number. Max 20 chars. |\n| `email` | string | Yes | Email address. Max 100 chars. |\n\n### Validation Rules\n- All fields are **required** and must be **non-empty**\n- `cedula` must not already exist in the database\n\n### Responses\n| Status | Condition |\n|---|---|\n| 201 Created | Customer created successfully |\n| 400 Bad Request | Missing or empty required fields |\n| 409 Conflict | Cédula already exists |\n| 500 Internal Server Error | DB error |"
